{"tid":1149383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵今日起一連三日推出半價乘車日","createTime":"2019-05-11T06:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T10:43:32.000Z","uid":164771,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0bcc01008a46f9e38531b10d44e7c8350b222aa5","tid":1149383,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"港鐵今日起一連三日推出特別車費日，以成人八達通乘搭港鐵，可享小童八達通票價優惠；有八達通特惠票價的乘客，本地車程車資只需繳一元。港鐵預計有1300萬人次受惠。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵是因應3月有列車相撞，令荃灣綫來往中環至金鐘站服務暫停兩日，因此推出特別車費日回饋乘客。推出特別車費期間，乘客可無限次使用優惠，並同時享有全月通加強版連接車程75折優惠及其他優惠。<br />\n<br />\n機場快綫、港鐵接駁巴士、往來羅湖及落馬洲站的車程及東鐵綫頭等車費則沒有優惠。"},{"pid":"3cbf1e67cbc3d1f7d894f00920510a75d21186a2","tid":1149383,"uid":120715,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"你係返工日子有事<br />\n但係星期六日送優惠<br />\n港鐵恰毒撚？！"},{"pid":"8b82dcb076cf8e7e1f95845dc5fc8ee8ed5a21bd","tid":1149383,"uid":188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"走水貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c3fa4edafae0c57bfcff1620aa0ce2c77e6e92","tid":1149383,"uid":72085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"施捨咩，放假仲特登去搭真係on9"},{"pid":"08a149d7f54b1334300bf4ddbb6720682e9a49f3","tid":1149383,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"冇出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d1d8e65dbb2692ec9d26c48de222009df54b02","tid":1149383,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"知唔知學生八達通搭頭等點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想試下"},{"pid":"b2036ffa2ccd03fcec9cf9816ab7c1bf00f2b6d6","tid":1149383,"uid":150033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:40:09.000Z","msg":"屌 唔翻工都唔撚記得半價"},{"pid":"6dfbeb4f8c036a9778a85071c03c4636ee5a930b","tid":1149383,"uid":228963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc